import Container from  "react-bootstrap/Container"

function Resources(){
    return (
        <Container>
            <Accordion defaultActiveKey="0">
                <Card>
                    <Card.Header>
                        <Accordion.Toggle as={Button} variant="link" eventKey="0">
                            Click Me!
                        </Accordion.Toggle>
                    </Card.Header>
                    <Accordion.Collapse>
                        <Card.Body>I am the content</Card.Body>
                    </Accordion.Collapse>
                </Card>
            </Accordion>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Resources
